{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ad778479b8","title":"周恩来陈伯达江青对中国京剧院的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5a50cebdd0","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":2,"articleId":"ad778479b8","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"关锋","id":"00506c3c84","type":"人物"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"金敬迈","id":"5d0a21e970","type":"人物"},{"name":"彭真","id":"5fd56865b0","type":"人物"},{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"杨成武","id":"e1397e909a","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"},{"name":"吴法宪","id":"fa1994871e","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"2b617b8936","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"中国剧协革命造反团、红代会中央戏剧学院红旗文艺兵团、中国青年艺术剧院东方红总部、剧协北京分会革命造反队《戏剧战报》第9期 1967年8月11日第1、2版"}],"contents":[{"id":"58aed1a221","type":"title","text":"周恩来陈伯达江青对中国京剧院的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70a0e8860f","type":"paragraph","text":"〖一九六七年八月二日晚，我们最敬爱的周总理、陈伯达同志、康生同志、杨成武同志、关锋同志、戚本禹同志、姚文元同志、叶群同志、吴法宪同志等中央首长再一次观看、审查了我院演出的革命现代京剧《红灯记》。同时观看的还有中央文革文艺组金敬迈同志、李英儒同志。演出完毕，在《大海航行靠舵手》的歌声中，钱浩梁、杜近芳、高玉倩、刘长瑜等十一位同志向中央首长献了《（红灯记）革命战斗兵团》鲜艳的红臂章。周总理、陈伯达同志、康生同志、江青同志、戚本禹同志、姚文元同志接见了参加《红灯记》演出的全体革命同志，并作了重要指示。接见时在座的还有金敬迈同志、李英儒同志。中央首长的身体都非常健康！江青同志身体非常健康！中央首长在百忙中抽出时间看我们的演出，接见我们并给以重要指示，是对我院全体革命同志的最大关怀，最大鼓舞！让我们一千遍一万遍地高呼：我们心中最红最红的红太阳毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！！","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e551991083","type":"paragraph","text":"现根据当时记录，将中央首长的重要指示整理如下。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"723197af22","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：孙洪勋，你练功了吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11ecf013f1","type":"paragraph","text":"孙洪勋：没有。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3921cbd25","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：都成了小胖子了。小胖子，每天要练功，要唱！八场的音乐改的好。（对钱浩梁）斗志更坚的“坚”字今天唱的不好，没有录音好。鸠山这个人的音乐搞得很优雅，鸠山应该是阴险、残暴、毒辣，现在搞得太优雅了。那个能创作的打鼓的同志来了吗？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a754cd902","type":"paragraph","text":"赓金群：来了。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d65b070e16","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：你可以找一找李劫夫同志，把鸠山的音乐研究一下。李金泉同志来了吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0822b80aac","type":"paragraph","text":"李金泉：来了。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d36476c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：要表现鸠山的阴险残暴是我早就提出来的。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"162f18ec27","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：我们还没有时间搞。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8065fcb399","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：鸠山的造型也很优雅，为什么把敌人搞得这么优雅，真是怪事！鸠山的音乐没有攻下来，应该攻克。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ae14e13d6","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：我们准备把“铁蹄踏遍……”一段唱掐掉。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d301c7cc5","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：这个戏越演越长了。第六场李玉和出场要唱出。唱四句，把精神实质唱出来。李玉和要估计敌人会用什么办法对付他，他要如何对付敌人，这四句话要把李玉和的这个精神准备唱出来，鸠山可以不出场，李玉和先出场。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1341fa8fdb","type":"paragraph","text":"这一场的舞台调度乱，层次不清，有重叠的地方，还没有以前的好。以前的缺点是把英雄人物死死地捆住了，但也有个好处，就是稳定。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8deabe4dbc","type":"paragraph","text":"这场戏要由李玉和唱开始，再由李玉和用唱来收住。《智取威虎山》我就要他们唱开始，唱结束的，他们还是攻下来了；“甘洒热血……”四句唱还是很好的。“魔高一尺，道高一丈”不好，没有力量。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8753e3161","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：这句话你们念倒了，应该是“道高一尺，魔高一丈”，你们念成“魔高一尺，道高一丈”。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffa4151aed","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：（对陈伯达同志）对吗？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"150e3961af","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：（点头）对！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b56a67883f","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：这句话要改，可以从鸠山那句话改。“苦海无边，回头是岸”，两句话要改掉，不要这样的话。李玉和上场情绪不对。应该唱四句，很沉着。一开始李玉和还是被请来的客人，要很沉着。现在是一来就一个人气鼓鼓地先坐下去了，应该是先斗智么，一开始还要装客人，直到后来叛徒出现了才显出英雄本色。主要是理解的不对。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5169d93dff","type":"paragraph","text":"粥棚一场，李玉和退着下场，心里是急着要退的，但表面是沉着的，可是又不要和敌人去顶，这也是理解的不对。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"157a86a0bb","type":"paragraph","text":"请总理讲一讲。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c47a8801c","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：这个戏就是鸠山动来动去的很不好，鸠山占的时间、音乐都太多了，重敌轻我了，敌人太夸张了，不要喧宾夺主。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"15ccc9a8c8","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：现在演三个钟头。要缩减，鸠山的戏要减，他的每一个动作都有音乐。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db6c439b7a","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：铁梅回家的一场演的不错，唱改的好，悲痛又壮烈，激情起来了。回家后哭的不好，这段戏很不好演，要注意悲壮。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5997cb6ade","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：这段近芳念的好。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"51b5f48755","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：那你可以向近芳学一学。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a23a5ab3b7","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：白口、唱都要悲要壮，第一句声音要低一些，这段在表演上要有一个过程。现在缺一个表演过程。今天唱的炸点了。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b205d8bb1f","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：“苦海无边，回头是岸”要改，“魔高一尺，道高一丈”这句不好，我想了一句，工作一忙又忘了。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f6a24b1be","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：总理有个意见：李玉和就义的时候，对鸠山说：“我要你考虑考虑”。“考虑”两个字不好。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d39557a684","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：李玉和对鸠山说：“中国共产党是杀不完的。我要你考虑考虑”。“考虑”这两个字不好。你要他考虑考虑是不是就不杀你了？不是要他考虑考虑，是要他知道中国共产党是杀不完的。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43e5a54ddc","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：改成我要你想一想，与鸠山说的话对着驳他。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"940bd58c60","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：高玉倩在第五场的唱法怎么都改了？","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ebe1e4cb6","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：没有改。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fbbdbe4b1c","type":"paragraph","text":"高玉倩：没有改，有一句“红灯再亮”改了。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4337c67e6a","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：不对，我怎么听着都改了。","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a1d0d6b42","type":"paragraph","text":"高玉倩：把“机密泄露”一句的唱法改了。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cdc9a926c","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：为什么改？","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f6bf73c91","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：根据观众来信改的，观众来信说这里翻高不合适，就改了。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a3c1abce8c","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：这是歌唱么，内心独白，为什么不可以翻高，完全可以照原来那样唱。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"27aa04276d","type":"paragraph","text":"高玉倩：观众来信说：把机密泄露了，可是唱到这里观众鼓掌叫好，不合适，就改了。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71d2776b4b","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：我们还要有民主集中制么，不通过我你们就改了，要不我怎么负责呀。（众笑）我还看见这样的意见，在上海有一个观众来信说：“象一个铁打的金刚”，是宣传迷信。其实不是那样，老百姓经常说象个金刚么。还是原来的唱法好，现在改了就不神气了。白口也不象以前神气了。刑场那一场的念白（指李奶奶）要逼得鸠山往后退，要一句比一句高，要逼得鸠山往后退，这样母亲的形象就高大了。现在的念不那么有力量。我过去讲过，主要是理解的不对。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9bc2a0f3c","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：第六场改散了，太零星了。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"51da7d9603","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：舞台调度乱，还是恢复原来的调度，把鸠山的动作去掉一些，不要沙发，炕要往前一些，还是要桌子，李玉和受刑后上场，还是要扶着椅子。原来的调度缺点是把英雄人物捆在一个地方，不合适，好处是稳定。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e0a4b43b4","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：现在的景也太敞了，有沙发，还有炕，后边还有个隔扇门，不太象。按日本的传统是不上炕的。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9895edac9","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：按日本的传统是坐在地上，那样观众就看不见了。","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cec1f28aad","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：也可以说鸠山中国化了，但是有炕也不太好。这场只是把原来跳舞等怪东西去掉不要了，就可以了。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"deb25a6d6e","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：李玉和上来加四句唱，这四句唱要和前场人物活动，要和后边戏的发展，呼应起来，前后有联系。《红灯记》最近演出了吗？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c99625526b","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：最近没有演出，演《智取威虎山》了。","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b918603c38","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：啊！你们也演《智取威虎山》了？谁演的？你演的吧？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87077414f4","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：是，请你审查审查。","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96f7c21a22","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：（问总理）怎么样？咱们看一次吧？","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8213dcf262","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：看一次吧。（经久不息的掌声）","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"748b440da3","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：一、四团合起来演的。","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc5e035271","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：应该合起来，把青年演员都合到一起。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e59468a2b","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：我演的甲字杨子荣，志孝演的少剑波。","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4aafc57d86","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：有B角吗？","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1d4133fa66","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：有，俞大陆演的杨子荣，孙岳演的少剑波。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"354851ec0a","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：俞大陆的嗓子能上去吗？","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35c77dec68","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：能。","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84ab990a7e","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：孙岳好了吗？","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9ba1af8e2","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：好了。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4718ffddc4","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：没有来，有演出。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db702a9d79","type":"paragraph","text":"群  众：今天休息，没有演出，俞大陆的嗓子也坏了。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2306e6fa43","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：演《智取威虎山》这种戏，要演一天休息一天。","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae7a0af7e8","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：俞大陆子个子矮一些。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3288ec727","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：个子矮没有关系，演的是气质，谭元寿不是个子也矮吗，各个有各人的演法。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f3985a742a","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：俞大陆艺术上有进步吗？","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49f6cb9e99","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：有进步。","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"355798f5c4","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：孙洪勋，（孙站起来）你成了小胖子了，你应该练功。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bfef62cd0d","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（小声对江青同志说）你今天已经批评人家两次了。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"42fc26e68d","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：他不练功我怎么不批评。","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45360867a7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对孙洪勋）对你的批评是对你的最大的鼓励。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5c7dde7dae","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：嗓子是可以练出来的，你可以练唱。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b62bb7e232","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：他过去在《智取威虎山》中演过少剑波。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dcc02d5386","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：你可以演杨子荣么。","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4e9dd5e10","type":"paragraph","text":"孙洪勋：好！","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ba069ddda","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：刘长瑜练功了吗？","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eed2c58b6a","type":"paragraph","text":"刘长瑜：没有。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6e09e1b8ce","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：高玉倩练功了吗？","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5c46ed8be","type":"paragraph","text":"高玉倩：没有。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"714ac29fce","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：（对钱浩梁）你练功了吗？","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1980d24fd","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：没有。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"55bbff2bb4","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：把青年演员都编到一起。演《海港》的李……？","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"04aac67a3b","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：李长春，现在在《智取威虎山》里演李勇奇。","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"006cfc0204","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：还可以演《海港》么。（对吴钰章）你演《海港》吧？","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"566913d4e4","type":"paragraph","text":"吴钰章：对。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"84bc372c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：（对刘长瑜）你的嗓子怎么有些沙哑？","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60af452b53","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：尽打内战，把嗓子都喊哑了。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"794b1df221","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：不要打内战，要一致对敌。","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8e7b90b00","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：敌人是谁？","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0e20f1b401","type":"paragraph","text":"群  众：刘少奇！","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3856826864","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：阿甲你们斗了吗？","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8e77ee6c6","type":"paragraph","text":"一群众：我们斗了二、三十次了。","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e4b08b3c2","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：阿甲有好些事情不告诉你们。过去每次看戏都是他坐在我旁边。这个人可厉害了，不好斗。","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7006203f42","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：彭真也放了不少毒么，你们可以和北京京剧团联合起来斗彭真么！","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7c041c80b","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：你们可以排《沙家浜》。","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3448f2d44b","type":"paragraph","text":"一群众：四团排了。","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b733944b29","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：二团现在演。","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"afa522feb0","type":"paragraph","text":"一群众：《奇袭白虎团》我们也学了。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"83984821fc","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：（对钱浩梁）《奇袭白虎团》谁排的？","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"088161cefe","type":"paragraph","text":"你演了吗？","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fde9742b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：一团没有排，三团学的。","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47cdf04a1f","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：谁演的？","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc3801128d","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：李光。","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5a60c389af","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：李光的嗓子能上来吗？","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9deeaf033","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：能。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"208b8026ee","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：我看你们不要这么多团了吧，把青年演员都合到一起。","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9f2c02106","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：这样你们就很有人材。","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5fff21ef0","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：袁世海解放了吧？","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90d2acbbd2","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：没有。","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48eec79baf","type":"paragraph","text":"一群众：我们还没有好好斗他呢！","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35765cebd6","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：袁世海比阿甲还好一点么，搞现代戏他还是跟着走的。应该给他记一功。旧社会过来的人么，你说呢，总理？","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2cdb8e11c","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：在改革的时候，还是积极参加的，三年前是个考验。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f34f11703","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：他不像阿甲那样厉害。阿甲这个人可厉害了！","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a408813b3","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：阿甲那是破坏！","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"85f94a4560","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：（对夏美珍）你练声了吗？","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4dc49c58e9","type":"paragraph","text":"夏美珍：没有。","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86e3bfec2d","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：你过去嗓子还是不错的么，你不练声，嗓子愈来愈坏。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d5257973b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对江青同志）近芳同志关于用嗓子问题，不是给你写了一封信吗。","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9e74625fc","type":"paragraph","text":"杜近芳：我看了中央乐团的办的一个刊物，上面有您关于用嗓子的指示。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"252ca9b842","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：不算什么指示，军队里对男声有些创造，张映哲是唱女高音的，也有假声，嘴也张不开。她吸取了一些民族唱法，用本嗓唱，就下来了，嘴也就张开了。（对刘长瑜）你的唱下来了没有？","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d908cc699","type":"paragraph","text":"刘长瑜：我现在念白基本上用大嗓，唱有时调门高就得用小嗓。","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fb4c75370","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：不要愈唱愈高，据人家说，李丽芳中音是假嗓，你可以试试大嗓。","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9749887ed1","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：你看我们的开打这样改成不成？","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0254cd7e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：开打不够精彩。","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"685dd75774","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：我们改了好几次了。","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d8f56ac5ee","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：你们可以组成一个武打小组，专门磨这一场戏。这场戏主要是磨刀人与叛徒两人对着，应该有精彩的。现在比过去好一些。过去人家人多，我们人少不合理。","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"191e58560d","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：过去我们两个，敌人五个。","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"beac1dd1dc","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：现在游击队，有多少人，有一班人吧？现在人多了，以多胜少是符合主席思想的，但是乱了一些。不一定都跳出来，有的可以藏在墙后射击，都暴露出来也不太合适，你们可以搞一个小组磨。你们都不练功，可不成。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34d8739b30","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：我已经给革命委员会提过了。","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f7f9d9c08","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：这不仅是京剧院的问题，是文艺口的普遍现象。李英儒同志要通知一下文艺口。","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a918a070b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（李英儒同志答应）","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f54949ab1","type":"paragraph","text":"刘长瑜：我们的小登子靠近一些了，你看怎么样？","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a966aa4e2a","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：这样合理，也亲近了。","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e05d84686f","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：《红灯记》有一个问题，从开始到现在我一直没有解决，跳车人死了李玉和怎么处理的？","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c8c39ef53","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：观众不会追问这些的。","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b3bab6005e","type":"paragraph","text":"康  生：没有看见出葬，埋在屋子里了吧。（总理和江青同志都笑了，众笑）","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"447fe70700","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：有人问我，我就这样回答。","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29d28afdf8","type":"paragraph","text":"还有个问题，过去我给你们这里一个人说过，现在再说一下，那边娃娃哭了，这边铁梅叫了一声：大娘，我给你们送东西”。这样就合理了，也可以敲一下墙，表现李家邻居关系是非常密切的。","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80e7880e1a","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：有些地方是不合理，铁梅放风应该到屋子外面去。","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c94d3d0d6","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：有个小院才好，东北都是有小院子的。","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b4f8da693","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：现在在屋子里说话我总感觉外边都听见了，景应该考虑重新设计，那样舞台上的东西挤满了，困难，细推敲，什么戏都事多了。","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70477fe2dc","type":"paragraph","text":"鸠山的音乐不搞好就先不要改。","index":143,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2199a95ec4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：好，同志们，今天就到这里吧！","index":144,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30425dd772","type":"paragraph","text":"钱浩梁：第四场我们有个想法，把鸠山的四句唱去掉，叛徒不打当场招供，就更暴露了叛徒的嘴脸了。","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"68a13b3f55","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：叛徒当场招，可以考虑。","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1466501f5d","type":"paragraph","text":"总  理：没打就招了，和后边李玉和被打，宁死不屈是个明显对照，这样好。","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48d6e4601d","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：六场乱，要恢复原来的，减掉一些鸠山的东西，一下子不容易解决。“苦海无边，回头是岸”几句就请康老想了。","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2956290528","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：你们经常给康老写信，催他。","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c325a645ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（呼口号，向江青同志学习！向江青同志致敬！我们心中最红最红的红太阳毛主席万岁！万万岁！）","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fc5f23cb02","type":"paragraph","text":"江  青：向同志们学习，向同志们致敬。","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c01d9b1951","type":"paragraph","text":"（众热烈鼓掌）","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b6653dd62","type":"paragraph","text":"（中国京剧院革命委员会供稿。附注：这个记录稿未经总理、陈伯达、康生、江青、戚本禹等同志审阅，如有错误，由整理者负责。）","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ad778479b8","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}